                                                                            <h4 class="panel-title">
                                                                                <a id="iforgotmypasswordtoaccessgemportalhowcaniresetit" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion_b" href="https://gem.gov.in/userFaqs#child_b1_1_1">I forgot my password to access GeM portal, how can I reset it? </a>
                                                                            </h4>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                        <div id="child_b1_1_1" class="child panel-collapse collapse ">
                                                                            <div class="panel-body">
                Please follow following steps to reset your password on GeM portal: <br>
1. Kindly visit https://gem.gov.in/ and click on Login, <br>
2. Click on "Forgot your Password" link, <br>
3. Enter your User Id, kindly note that User Id is case sensitive, <br>
4. Type the Characters displayed in the captcha box, press SUBMIT, <br>
5. An E-mail will be sent to your registered E-mail ID with link to Reset password, <br>
6. Click on Reset Link in your E-mail, and Enter new password and confirm the same, Press SUBMIT. <br>
Kindly note that your Password must be of 8-20 characters- 1 upper case letter, 1 lower case letter, number, and a special character.                                                                            </div>
